'''伯德·米勒'''（{{lang-en|Bode Miller}}，{{IPAc-en|ˈ|b|oʊ|d|iː}}，{{bd|1977年|10月12日}}），[[美國|美國]]高山滑雪世界盃運動員。他在世界盃奪得33個冠軍，使他被稱為世界盃最佳運動員之一，他也成為五位在五個項目都奪冠的運動員之一。<ref>{{Cite news| last = Futterman| first = Matthew| title = Bode Miller Wins Gold in Super Combined| newspaper = [[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]]| date = February 22, 2010| url = http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052748704751304575079810752278940.html?mod=WSJ_hpp_LEFTTopStories| accessdate = March 14, 2010| archive-date = 2012-11-10| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121110095034/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052748704751304575079810752278940.html?mod=WSJ_hpp_LEFTTopStories| dead-url = no}}</ref>

2018年6月9日，米勒的19個月大女兒在南加州[[橙縣_(加利福尼亞州)|橙縣]]鄰居的泳池遇溺，6月10日不治。米勒另有3個孩子。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.espn.com/olympics/story/_/id/23765505/olympian-bode-miller-19-month-old-daughter-dies-drowning |title=19-month-old daughter of Olympic skier Bode Miller drowns in pool |website=espn.com |date= |accessdate=2018-06-12 |archive-date=2018-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612100320/http://www.espn.com/olympics/story/_/id/23765505/olympian-bode-miller-19-month-old-daughter-dies-drowning |dead-url=no }}</ref>

